Icons

Bootstrap Default Icons Included.

Custom iconic font genarated by https://icomoon.io/app/
Font Name: iconic
Total Icons : 1963
Included Popular Icon fonts : Fontawesome , Feather , Iconic , Material Design Icons, Entypo+

This font easyly customize by uploading selection.json to the app. selection.json file located under fonts directory.
